      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in solid shape and has been well-loved, making it the perfect companion for your daily commutes or weekend getaways. It runs great and is ready to hit the road with a new owner today! I've priced it to move quickly, so come take a look and see for yourself\u2014you're going to love it!",
