    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a driver-focused example featuring the iconic S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering linear power through six individual throttle bodies and a crisp 6-speed Getrag manual transmission. The engine exhibits strong compression across all cylinders, with the critical double-VANOS system recently serviced for optimal cam timing. Chassis dynamics are sharp, aided by a factory limited-slip differential and reinforced rear subframe mounts to ensure structural integrity under lateral load. Suspension remains taut with refreshed bushings, while the cross-drilled rotors provide consistent bite. A mechanically sound specimen for the purist who values high-revving atmospheric performance over garage-queen status.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
