    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Up for sale is a remarkably well-maintained vehicle that strikes the perfect balance between performance and daily utility. The exterior paint retains a high-gloss finish, showing only the lightest evidence of careful use, such as minor stone chips on the lower valance. The body panels are straight with consistent gaps throughout. Inside, the interior remains in excellent shape; the upholstery is free of tears or significant stains, and the dashboard remains crack-free. All power features, including the windows, sunroof, and premium audio system, are fully operational. Mechanically, this car is robust. It has been serviced at regular intervals, with a recent cooling system flush and brake pad replacement just performed. The engine idles quietly and provides smooth power delivery, while the suspension remains tight and responsive over bumps. This is a non-smoker vehicle that has been primarily garage-kept. I have a folder of maintenance receipts ready for the buyer to review, ensuring complete transparency regarding its history. It is a turn-key example ready for its next owner.",
